<script type="text/javascript">
	$('#logo').hide();
</script>

<section id="welcome-message">
	<h1 id="index-title">OUTFIT HUNT</h1>
	<h2>發現衣服更多實用穿法</h2>
</section>

<section id="step-introduction">
  <h3>三步驟  取得穿搭建議</h3>
  <div class="step-icons-all">
    <div class="all-steps">
      <div class="step-icon">
        <span>1</span>
      </div>
      <span>上傳衣服</span>
    </div>
    <div class="all-steps">
      <div class="step-icon">
        <span>2</span>
      </div>
      <span>送出問題</span>
    </div>
    <div class="all-steps">
      <div class="step-icon">
        <span>3</span>
      </div>
      <span>收到穿搭</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="email-area">
  <%= form_for @asker do |f| %>
    <section class="input-area">
      <h4>↓ 開始免費試用 ↓</h4>
      <div class="email-bar">
        <div class="icon-person"><%= image_tag image_url('icon-person.png')%></div>
        <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, placeholder: "E-mail", class: "form-control" %>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="action">
      <%= f.submit "取得穿搭建議", class: "start btn btn-next"%>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</section>

<section class="info-area">
  <div class="service-info">
    <h3>服務說明</h3>
    <h4>☛ 啟動試用</h4>
    <p>啟動試用服務，就能收到屬於妳的實用穿搭。</p>

    <h4>☛ 有件衣服不會搭</h4>
    <p>當妳有一件不知該怎麼搭配的衣服，堆著又佔空間，丟掉浪費錢，妳就可以使用我們的網站。</p>

    <h4>☛ 拍照上傳</h4>
    <p>首先為了提供妳合適的搭法，請將這件衣服拍照拍上傳給我們。</p>

    <h4>☛ 不知道搭什麼</h4>
    <p>讓我們知道這件衣服穿搭上的困擾。</p>

    <h4>☛ 精準服裝掃描分析</h4>
    <p>根據妳上傳的衣服、提出的困擾，透過程式辨識及穿搭達人交叉比對</p>

    <h4>☛ 收到屬於妳的實用穿搭馬上派上用場。</h4>
  </div>
</section>

<%= render partial: '/icon' %>
